、配置、处理租务和租期服务等一系列事务……每位管家大约负责60套自如友家的房屋，为160位租客提供服务，每天回应40位租客的电话。</p><p>“Ziroom has a dedicated team of housekeepers. As product managers of Ziroom’s properties, the housekeepers are responsible for organizing andcoordinating in the design, furnishing, renting, and services of theproperties. … Each housekeeper is in charge of over 60suites of Ziroom Youjia properties, serving more than 160 Ziroomers. Theyrespond to over 40 customer calls a day.”</p><p>以上内容均摘自哈佛商业案例</p>'
